{"word":"ἐπιχειλής","slug":"ἐπιχειλής","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n41616\" key=\"e)pixeilh/s\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἐπιχειλής</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ές</itype>, (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">χεῖλος</etym>) <sense id=\"n41616.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">on</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">at the lips,</tr_> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">γλῶσσα ἐ.</foreign> a <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">ready, chattering</tr_> tongue, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0542.tlg001:6:120\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Poll.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.120</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n41616.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">full up to the rim</tr_> (i.e. not quite full, as the rim was deep), of Themistocles, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἐποίησεν τὴν πόλιν ἡμῶν μεστήν, εὑρὼν ἐπιχειλῆ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg002.perseus-grc1:814\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Eq.\">Eq.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">814</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n41616.2\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> later, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">brim-full,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">πίθος ἐ. τῶν ἀγαθῶν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg2001.tlg013:174d\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Them.\">Them.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Or.\">Or.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">13.174d</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg2001.tlg008:115a\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">8.115a</biblScope> </bibl>: metaph., <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">πλήρεις καὶ ἐ. ἁμαρτίαι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0018.tlg001:1:517\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ph.\">Ph.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.517</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"III\" id=\"n41616.3\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">with the lips drawn in,</tr_> <abbr TEIform=\"abbr\">like</abbr> old people, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0640.tlg001:3:55\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Alciphr.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.55</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}